## Summary
This documentation explains how to create and use Calculations in Amplitude, which transform events or event properties into user properties for segmentation. It details the three types of calculation properties (Event Count, Aggregation, First/Last Value), how to create and delete them, and how to use them in campaigns and analytics as filters or for external destination syncing.

